[ti:Row Row Row Your Boat]
[ar:Children's Nursery Rhyme]
[al:Little English Star]

[00:00.00]Row, row, row your boat
[00:02.72]Gently down the stream
[00:05.36]Merrily, merrily, merrily, merrily
[00:08.74]Life is but a dream
[00:11.28]Row, row, row your boat
[00:13.96]Gently down the brook
[00:16.42]If you see a crocodile
[00:18.62]Don't forget to shout!
